2. Prove or reject the room-level idempotency hypothesis with one bounded synthetic event.
3. Fix scheduling and prove one judge write before starting the retro or A/B steps.
4. Inventory and migrate legacy telemetry rows, restore auth-only sessions, retire the second Convex deployer, and verify a live writer.

